Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:08.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}どこかで呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:10.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}近づいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:13.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}真っ白な世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:18.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}たった一つだけの約束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.90,0:24:30.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}きっと忘れないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.44,0:24:34.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}二人過ごした永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:37.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}照れ臭そうに手招く
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.83,0:24:41.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}無邪気な時の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:44.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}言葉で伝えるには
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.75,0:24:48.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}未完成な感情です
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.25,0:24:52.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}運命を嘆くほど
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.13,0:24:56.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}私たち弱くはない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.60,0:24:59.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}ねぇそうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.39,0:25:01.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}どこかで呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.81,0:25:03.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}動き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.69,0:25:06.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}選び取る答えに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.81,0:25:10.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}心ちぎれそうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.98,0:25:14.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}守りたいものがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.74,0:25:18.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}ためらいの朝　迷いの夜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.41,0:25:21.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}もし手を離しても
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.45,0:25:27.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}必ずたどり着くと信じてます
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.84,0:25:34.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}私を呼ぶ声が聞こえてる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:08.34,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在某处呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:10.09,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}离我近点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:13.09,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在纯白的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:18.52,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}只有一个承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.90,0:24:30.44,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我相信你不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.44,0:24:34.32,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我们一起度过的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:37.83,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}你的招呼让我害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.83,0:24:41.91,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在纯真的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:44.75,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}要我用言语说明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.75,0:24:48.80,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}是一种不完整的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.25,0:24:52.13,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}命运的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.13,0:24:56.60,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我们的关系会更脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.60,0:24:59.39,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}嘿，对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.39,0:25:01.81,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在某处呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.81,0:25:03.69,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}快点来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.69,0:25:06.61,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我不知道怎么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.81,0:25:10.98,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}即使我放下我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.98,0:25:14.74,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}因为有想要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.74,0:25:18.41,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}早上的混乱，晚上的犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.41,0:25:21.45,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}就算放开你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.45,0:25:27.92,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我相信你会到达那里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.84,0:25:34.09,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}你能听见我的心声吗
